00:10:41.608 --> 00:10:46.413 align:start position:27% line:-2
LEGOデモでご覧のとおり
認識して追加します

00:10:47.915 --> 00:10:50.918 align:start position:27% line:-2
このゲームは
World Mapの共有で

00:10:51.018 --> 00:10:54.788 align:start position:36% line:-2
